name: Verify the report data after the respective filters are added

testSteps.description: Given underwriter has ability to create quote for LOB Workers Compensation

And with Program and MarketSegment as
| Program | MarketSegment |
| Amazon | Amazon |
And user navigates to report 'Quote Pending Issuance' and opens filter edits

And provides data as
| Quote Effective Date Range - Start | Program | MarketSegment | UnderwritingManager |
|  | Amazon | Amazon | Kartik |
When underwriter searches for the quote
Then the quote created above should be searched
Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And user navigates to report 'Quote Pending Issuance' and opens filter edits

And provides data as
| Quote Effective Date Range - Start | Program | MarketSegment | UnderwritingManager |
|  | Amazon | Amazon | Kartik |
When underwriter searches for the quote
Then the quote matching the above criteria should be displayed

And all the quotes in the search result should have the data
| Program | MarketSegment | UnderwritingManager |
| Amazon | Amazon | Kartik |
